@Kecn_S @lasaintolga Method:
Grind spices (except cardamon which I keep whole). Dry toast them in a saucepan, pop them in a muslin bag with the tea, then bring water and milk to a simmer, add tea/spice bag and let it simmer for 3-4 minutes. Take off the heat add a tspn of raw ginger juice. Enjoy

@Kecn_S @lasaintolga Ingredients:
1 cinnamon stick
1 cardamon pod
4-5 cloves
1/2 tspn of black peppercorns
2 star anise pods
1 heaped tspn organic black tea
1/2 tspn jasmine tea
1 espresso shot
100ml water
300ml milk
